         <head>OLD COUNSEL
            OF THE YOUNG MASTER OF A WRECKED 
            CALIFORNIA CLIPPER.</head>
         <lg>
            <l>COME out of the Golden Gate,</l>
            <l rend="indent">Go round the Horn with streamers,</l>
            <l>Carry royals early and late ;</l>
            <l>But, brother, be not over-elate-</l>
            <l>All hands save ship ! has startled dreamers.</l>
         </lg>
